<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们围着妈妈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们知道爸爸因为公司有事突然离开了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23866</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是为什么妈妈这么伤心呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸什么时候才能回来呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31613</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “这件事就不要再问了。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31614</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，我不能回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请你们也不要问其他人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 彼得红着脸低下头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “答应我，好吗？”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44934</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我问了露丝。”彼得说，“对不起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “她说了什么？”妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “她说我们很快就会知道了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “你们什么都不需要知道。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“因为这是公事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们知道什么是公事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “不知道。”鲍比说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“和政府有关吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>爸爸在政府部门工作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “是的。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，一切都会好起来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “妈妈，你也别担心！”菲利斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会很乖的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  妈妈叹了口气，亲了亲他们。孩子们去睡觉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100133</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来的几个星期，妈妈经常出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100134</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾玛姨妈来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾玛姨妈比妈妈大很多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她总是在缝衣服，很无趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们更喜欢和仆人们在一起，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为他们更有趣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果厨师心情好，还会唱歌给他们听。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，彼得设计了一个小陷阱 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把一桶面粉放在浴室门上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>露丝开门的时候，面粉全洒在她的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “我会告诉夫人的！”露丝生气地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你不注意一点，就会跟你爸爸一样！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  彼得不知道她在说什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 一天早上，妈妈下楼来吃早餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她笑着对孩子们说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158839</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“宝贝们，我们要离开这里，去村庄生活了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158840</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们会搬到一个白色的小房子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们一定会喜欢的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来的一个星期，大家都忙着收拾行李。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们打包了碗筷、地毯、锅具和烛台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “妈妈，这个要带走吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比指着一个漂亮的衣柜问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我们不能带走所有的东西。”妈妈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “可是我们要带走的东西都很难看。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “我们只能带走有用的东西。”妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 鲍比 ，我们现在没有那么多钱了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  第二天， 他们出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈带着孩子们去了火车站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211455</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾玛姨妈在站台向他们挥手告别。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们很开心，因为他们再也不会见到无趣的姨妈了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车开了，他们向着新家出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一开始，孩子们很开心地一直往窗外看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238300</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但天越来越黑，孩子们也越来越困了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来，妈妈轻轻地叫醒他们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244854</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们到了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比、菲利斯和彼得在站台上冷得发抖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>火车开了，孩子们看着火车离开车站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是他们在铁路上看到的第一辆火车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们现在还不知道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁路很快就会成为对他们来说很特别的东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>  “走吧。” 妈妈说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275273</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们得走过去。这里没有出租车。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一辆马车载着他们的行李。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们和妈妈走在马车后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>晚上又黑又冷，路上都是泥。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后妈妈终于说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们到了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>